subject: Rajasthan History
question_en: Which king is associated with the city of Jodhpur?
question_hi: जोधपुर के लैंग्डर कौन सा है।
explanation_en: Rao Jodha is associated with the city of Jodhpur. He was the founder of the city and the Meera Fort.
